WEBVTT

00:00:00.644 --> 00:00:02.478
OK, so, confession:

00:00:02.502 --> 00:00:07.103
I've always been weirdly
obsessed with advertising.

00:00:08.238 --> 00:00:11.306
I remember watching
Saturday morning cartoons,

00:00:11.330 --> 00:00:13.463
paying more attention to the commercials

00:00:13.487 --> 00:00:14.794
than to the shows,

00:00:14.818 --> 00:00:17.908
trying to figure out how they were trying
to get inside my head.

00:00:17.932 --> 00:00:20.011
Ultimately, that led me to my dream job.

00:00:20.035 --> 00:00:23.313
I became a partner
at a big New York ad agency.

00:00:23.337 --> 00:00:29.526
But then, all of that suddenly changed
on February 23, 1997,

00:00:29.550 --> 00:00:32.898
when my little brother Matt
was shot in the head